USAGE

Load the modules you want or the full shrike.js into your page with a <script> tag:
<script type="text/javascript" src="shrike.js"></script>




MODULES

core.js
is the Shrike core and is required by all other modules. Requires the Puma CSS selector engine.

events.js
is the event system, with Shrike.addEvent/removeEvent, Shrike.ready, Shrike.on, and Shrike.off.

ajax.js
contains the Ajax functionality.

animation.js
contains animation and drag&drop functionality. Requires events.js.

shrike.js
contains all of the above modules and the Puma CSS selector engine.




FUNCTIONS

See the docs/ folder, which isn't finished yet. I recommend just browsing the source, it's pretty straightforward.